# Dandomain Theme Development

## Systemarkitektur

| Komponent | Teknologi |
|-----------|-----------|
| Template engine | Smarty 3 (PHP-baseret, `.tpl` filer) |
| Styling | SCSS + Compass mixins |
| Build | Grunt (ældre temaer) / Gulp 5 + Tailwind CSS 4 (nyere temaer) |
| Frontend JS | AngularJS 1.4.3 + jQuery |
| CSS grid | 24-kolonne responsivt system |
| Biblioteker | Fancybox, Select2, Owl Carousel |

Blueprint-reference: `blueprints/template007_1/` indeholder et komplet fungerende tema med alle mønstre.

---

## Smarty Nøglemønstre

### Assets

```smarty
{addLink href='assets/css/template.css'}
{addLink href='assets/css/print.css' media='print'}
{addScript src='assets/js/app.js'}
```

### Hent en samling (liste af entiteter)

```smarty
{collection assign=products controller=productList categoryId=$page.categoryId pageSize=12}
{foreach $products as $product}
    <h2>{$product->Title}</h2>
    <a href="{$product->Link}">{$product->Title}</a>
{/foreach}
```

### Hent en enkelt entitet

```smarty
{entity assign=product controller=product id=$page.productId}
{$product->Title}
{$product->Description}
```

### Hent controller-instans

```smarty
{controller assign=catCtrl type=productCategory}
{$catCtrl->link($category->Id)}
```

### Include partials

```smarty
{include file='modules/product/product-list.tpl' productlist=$products}
{include file='partials/top.tpl'}
{include file="modules/widgets/cookie/cookie.tpl"}
```

### Platform hooks (i index.tpl)

```smarty
<head>
    {head_include}
</head>
<body ...>
    {body_include}
    {pageTypeInclude}
```

### Hjælpere

```smarty
{breadcrumbs}
{placeholdImage width=160 height=120}
{csrf}
{img src=$product->Image width=160 height=120 alt=$product->Title}
```

### Sidetype-betingelser

```smarty
{if $page.isFrontPage}...{/if}
{if $page.type == 'product' && count($page.paths) == 1}
    {* Produktkategori *}
{elseif $page.type == 'product' && count($page.paths) == 2}
    {* Produktside *}
{/if}
{if $general.isShop}...{/if}
```

