## Grid-system (24-kolonne)

4 breakpoints – **total kolonner per breakpoint**:

| Breakpoint | Prefix | Skærmbredde | Max kolonner |
|------------|--------|-------------|--------------|
| Small | `col-s-` | 0–480px | 4 |
| Medium | `col-m-` | 480–768px | 12 |
| Large | `col-l-` | 768–960px | 12 |
| XLarge | `col-xl-` | 960px+ | 24 |

```html
<!-- Fuld bredde -->
<div class="col-s-4 col-m-12 col-l-12 col-xl-24">...</div>

<!-- Halvt layout (xl) -->
<div class="col-s-4 col-m-6 col-l-6 col-xl-12">...</div>

<!-- Container -->
<div class="container with-xlarge">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-s-4 col-m-12 col-l-12 col-xl-24">...</div>
    </div>
</div>
```

