## Globale Template-variable

### $page

```smarty
$page.type          {* 'text', 'product', 'news', 'blog', 'cart', 'checkout' *}
$page.id
$page.name
$page.title
$page.headline
$page.isFrontPage   {* bool *}
$page.isProduct     {* bool *}
$page.isCart        {* bool *}
$page.isCheckout    {* bool *}
$page.productId     {* aktuelt produkt-ID *}
$page.categoryId    {* aktuel kategori-ID *}
$page.paths         {* array af URL-segmenter *}
$page.breadcrumbs   {* array *}
```

### $general

```smarty
$general.isShop             {* bool - er det en shop? *}
$general.languageIso639     {* 'da', 'en', 'no', 'sv' *}
$general.domain
$general.dateFormat
$general.shopId
