## SCSS-struktur

```
source/
├── scss/
│   ├── template.scss       ← Hoved-entry (importerer alt)
│   ├── globals/
│   │   ├── _settings.scss  ← Breakpoints, farver, variabler
│   │   └── _mixins.scss    ← Hjælper-mixins
│   ├── framework/          ← Grid, reset, base-styles
│   └── modules/            ← Komponent-specifik SCSS
```

Compass-mixins bruges (via `compass-mixins-template`):
```scss
@include border-radius(4px);
@include box-shadow(0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.1));
@include transition(all .3s ease);
```

---

## Blueprint Modulstruktur

```
modules/
├── framework/      ← Email-skabeloner, print-layout
├── product/        ← product.tpl, product-list.tpl, product-entity.tpl
├── column/         ← Sidebar-bokse (module-cart, module-news osv.)
├── widgets/        ← cookie, usp, slick, sidebar, notification
├── calendar/
├── blog/ (hvis til stede)
├── form/
├── contact/
├── gallery/
├── sitemap/
└── notfound/
partials/
├── top.tpl         ← Header
└── footer.tpl      ← Footer
```

**Konvention**: PageType-filer hedder det samme som sidetypens navn, f.eks. `modules/product/product.tpl` vises når `$page.type == 'product'`.

